{"tid":2162563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「泛民留任為錢」係藍絲思維","createTime":"2020-08-18T07:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T01:01:40.000Z","uid":331972,"like":63,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"15a2148752ae67b9d2e3a723514c11ca75e70d0a","tid":2162563,"uid":331972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"對於泛民議員應該杯葛非法議會定留任，我個人係冇強烈既取態<br />\n杯葛同留任都各有利弊，我唔覺得有一個壓倒性較佳嘅選擇，所以個人覺得最好嘅方法係搞公投決定去留<br />\n<br />\n但係我留意到連登最近成日出現「泛民留任係為錢」既犬儒主義論調<br />\n我諗咁樣講嘅巴絲打唔係PR五毛，而係真心相信泛民議員留任係單純為咗錢<br />\n但其實咁樣諗係極度危險，只係自我設限、故步自封，將一切自己唔認同唔理解嘅價值貶低成為咗自己私利嘅行徑<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅諗法其實同藍絲嘅「收錢論」冇分別：<br />\n「班暴徒係收咗錢去掟磚」、「黃之鋒收咗美國佬錢搞亂香港」、「啲暴徒放咗火咪有得移民去美國囉」背後反映嘅心態就係：冇人會為咗正義、民主而挺身而出，一切只係比金錢利益驅動<br />\n當有人反駁自己，就話對方比「美國佬」、「黃屍」洗咗腦<br />\n<br />\n其實「泛民為錢留任」同藍絲既論調係同出一轍<br />\n當泛民話唔留任議會冇咗反對聲音，「為錢派」就話呢個係藉口，佢地實則只係為錢（若然佢地係真心覺得留守議會有價值呢？）<br />\n當有人為泛民留任辯護，「為錢派」就覺得對方愚昧無知<br />\n<br />\n「為錢論」其實係萬能Key，唔駛用腦就否定曬任何嘢<br />\n美國幫我地係為經濟利益<br />\n許智峯、朱凱迪議會抗爭係為咗下屆參選拎每個月十萬蚊人工<br />\n戴耀廷發起佔中、搞初選係為出名為拎捐款<br />\n鄺神係前線比人打到頭破血流又係搏上鏡為咗錢<br />\n本土派參選又係為咗十萬蚊人工<br />\n區議員當初參選又係為咗錢⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話泛民議員留任係完全冇利益計算（e.g. 人工可能係考慮因素之一；亦可能想喺呢一年搏表現爭取返選民嘅支持扭轉返初選嘅劣勢）<br />\n大家亦可以批評佢地留任嘅理據唔合理（e.g. 實際上不可行、因小失大）<br />\n但面對唔同意見嘅聲音，希望各位巴絲打嘗試比啲胸襟咁去諗：<span class=\"red\">對方可能係真誠地覺得咁樣對件事最好，我可以點說服對方呢？</span> （就算你覺得對方係完全為咗錢，都嘗試咁諗，諗下對對方論點最有利既論據係咩）<br />\n一切「對方係為咗錢」、「佢蠢先咁諗」\b、「佢肯定係比人洗腦」嘅諗法都無助理性溝通"},{"pid":"30d9e1727875d4ea1e138ceca3f6dbc9efb039b2","tid":2162563,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":13,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"唔為錢唔通為藝術情操咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7409f4daff680142e9a2af764c459babe885980","tid":2162563,"uid":43062,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"一開口就話為十萬大佬真係討論唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b22e0ddb22f0d9e5c46c520c78c8cfb2a2c091c","tid":2162563,"uid":331972,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"加多句：<br />\n如果啲議員係<span class=\"red\">單純</span>為錢嘅點解唔加入建制派？"},{"pid":"0c6d343a154b165ab3dd7f03f643e2a89b39eae9","tid":2162563,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30d9e1727875d4ea1e138ceca3f6dbc9efb039b2","tid":2162563,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":13,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"唔為錢唔通為藝術情操咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢地勤勤力力咁返工都可以話為理想，除咗慢必。有邊個出席率係正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970134741ff3fc06ebe8e1cf17e159a49b960640","tid":2162563,"uid":21772,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"留低最大嘅理由真係得錢，唔係話為錢唔得，但連認都唔敢認又真係好難講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c375a156b18742334c827b59063f108d90bfc0","tid":2162563,"uid":94516,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b22e0ddb22f0d9e5c46c520c78c8cfb2a2c091c","tid":2162563,"uid":331972,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"加多句：<br />\n如果啲議員係<span class=\"red\">單純</span>為錢嘅點解唔加入建制派？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:49:03.000Z","msg":"你咪睇吓羅致光，唔先做反對派。點叫高價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00432937dc44f93ed3f662f2060845eba97d3f47","tid":2162563,"uid":309558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"既然係咁就一於全體泛民捐一半糧<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知佢哋又咩原因會唔肯呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d477249f13cf6fed83de00b57c734cde5b4bf540","tid":2162563,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"970134741ff3fc06ebe8e1cf17e159a49b960640","tid":2162563,"uid":21772,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"留低最大嘅理由真係得錢，唔係話為錢唔得，但連認都唔敢認又真係好難講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"雞：我為幫廣大既男性解決性需要 我係一個藝術性工作者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a36776b5d88f8edde112f8fd47556f54405163","tid":2162563,"uid":196087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n唔認同泛民留任，咪支持海外手足建立海外議會，課金，狂打國際線宣告舊議會已死另立議會囉<br />\n流亡議會唔係你講就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要有足夠民意基礎，但依樣野唔係靠屌泛民就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你幾時見袁公係用90%時間屌泛民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係做實事嘅，揀好自己立場就諗有咩可以做啦<br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺得留任影響外國觀感<br />\n除非啲議員受到實質人身威脅，否則都好難加速外國反應"},{"pid":"6dd110eebcfe879064a33fd0536df79c411eaf57","tid":2162563,"uid":94516,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"成日話為錢點解唔入建制<br />\n一，你話入就入咩，咁多人投共點解要簡你？<br />\n二，人地建制真係要做野架。一黎阿爺吹雞真係要返工投票，仲有蛇齋餅糉呢，民建聯落區絕對多過泛民，可以唔返工但有糧出，出面有咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5427106af7b8114b081b13d2babbfc72913bf15","tid":2162563,"uid":331972,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"970134741ff3fc06ebe8e1cf17e159a49b960640","tid":2162563,"uid":21772,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"留低最大嘅理由真係得錢，唔係話為錢唔得，但連認都唔敢認又真係好難講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"我覺得一旦認定對方最大理由係為咗錢就令成件事冇曬討論空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你不如去將佢地諗成一班唔係為錢既聖人（無論你幾咁強烈認為對方真係為咗錢），諗下點解佢地會揀留守，再分析下佢地既理由夠唔夠說服力<br />\n可能你最後都會得出同樣既結論，但咁既結論比純粹認定對方係為錢留任而得出既結論更有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184d6606d6b159487dd74d98e05e725eb3618563","tid":2162563,"uid":94516,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5427106af7b8114b081b13d2babbfc72913bf15","tid":2162563,"uid":331972,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"970134741ff3fc06ebe8e1cf17e159a49b960640","tid":2162563,"uid":21772,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"留低最大嘅理由真係得錢，唔係話為錢唔得，但連認都唔敢認又真係好難講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"我覺得一旦認定對方最大理由係為咗錢就令成件事冇曬討論空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你不如去將佢地諗成一班唔係為錢既聖人（無論你幾咁強烈認為對方真係為咗錢），諗下點解佢地會揀留守，再分析下佢地既理由夠唔夠說服力<br />\n可能你最後都會得出同樣既結論，但咁既結論比純粹認定對方係為錢留任而得出既結論更有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"留條春咩，叫佢地返齊工先講野啦屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/12/hndgKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2FhndgKk.png&h=3ed0facf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/12/Z2myWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2FZ2m